detaileddescription.para: Set entity name (skin name for spine, entity name for spriter). BIND_AS_PROPERTY

briefdescription.para: Set animation by name and loop mode.
Reload sprite and spriter data on device reset.
Animated sprite component, it uses to play animation created by Spine (http://www.esotericsoftware.com) and Spriter (http://www.brashmonkey.com/).
